in his home country was owned

97
00:03:41,270 --> 00:03:42,270
by 20% of the population.

98
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,360
This principle holds true
nearly 200 years later

99
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,480
and can even be applied
to different topics

100
00:03:48,350 --> 00:03:49,350
such as business or athletics.

