important at the bottom.

113
00:04:23,490 --> 00:04:24,490
Finally, cross out 80% of
your tasks from the bottom

114
00:04:26,790 --> 00:04:27,790
so that you're only left with the top 20%.

115
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,440
By doing this, you will
improve your productivity

116
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,960
and efficiency by focusing all
of your efforts on the tasks

117
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,400
that will actually yield success.

